gazine/article/0,9171,844255,00.html \"The Master Builder\"] (obituary of Cardinal Spellman).\n\n== External links ==\n{{Commons category|Francis Spellman}}\n* [http://www.milarch.org/ Archdiocese for the Military Services, USA], official website\n* [http://www.gcatholic.org/dioceses/diocese/unit0.htm Archdiocese for the Military Services of the United States]. GCatholic.org. Retrieved 2010-08-20.\n* [http://vault.fbi.gov/Cardinal%20Francis%20Spellman FBI file on Cardinal Spellman]\n* [https://www.archny.org/ Roman Catholic Archdiocese of New York], official website\n\n{{s-start}}\n{{s-rel|ca}}\n\n{{s-bef| before = See Created }}\n{{s-ttl| title = Titular Bishop of Sila\n       | years = 1932\u20131939 }}\n{{s-aft| after = [[Thomas Arthur Connolly]] }}\n\n{{s-bef| rows = 2 |before = [[Patrick Joseph Hayes]] }}\n{{s-ttl| title  = [[Archdiocese of New York|Archbishop of New York]]\n       | years  = 1939\u20131967 }}\n{{s-aft| rows   = 3 | after  = [[Terence Cooke]] }}\n\n{{s-ttl| title  = [[Roman Catholic Archdiocese for the Military Services|Apostolic Vicar for the Military Services]]\n       | years  = 1939\u20131967 }}\n\n{{s-bef| before = [[Pope Pius XII|Eugenio Pacelli]] }}\n{{s-ttl| title = [[Santi Giovanni e Paolo, Rome|Cardinal-Priest of Santi Giovanni e Paolo]]\n       | years = 1946\u20131967 }}\n{{S-end}}\n{{Roman Catholic Archdiocese of New York}}\n{{Pope Pius XII}}\n{{Roman Catholic Military Ordinariates}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Spellman, Francis}}\n[[Category:1889 births]]\n[[Category:1967 deaths]]\n[[Category:20th-century Roman Catholic archbishops]]\n[[Category:American anti-communists]]\n[[Category:American cardinals]]\n[[Category:American military chaplains]]\n[[Category:American Philatelic Society]]\n[[Category:American Roman Catholic clergy of Irish descent]]\n[[Category:Burials at St. Patrick's Cathedral (Manhattan)]]\n[[Category:Cardinals created by Pope Pius XII]]\n[[Category:Catholics from Massachusetts]]\n[[Category:Fordham U