ebsite=[[Xbox]] |archivedate=23 March 2018 |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20180323151521/https://news.xbox.com/en-us/2017/02/23/observer-coming-soon-xbox-one/ |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"objects\">{{cite video |url=http://www.ign.com/videos/2017/06/22/observer-gameplay-hidden-horror-developer-walkthrough |title=Observer Gameplay: Hidden Horror Developer Walkthrough |date=22 June 2017 |website=[[IGN]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170626014955/http://www.ign.com/videos/2017/06/22/observer-gameplay-hidden-horror-developer-walkthrough |archive-date=26 June 2017 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"unr341\">{{cite web |url=https://www.unrealengine.com/en-US/blog/unreal-engine-developers-were-everywhere-at-e3-2017 |title=Unreal Engine Developers Were Everywhere at E3 2017 |first=Daniel |last=Kayser |date=23 June 2017 |website=[[Unreal Engine]] |archivedate=23 March 2018 |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20180323151752/https://www.unrealengine.com/en-US/blog/unreal-engine-developers-were-everywhere-at-e3-2017 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"catharsis\">{{cite web |url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/pressreleases/300512/Bloober_Team_Breaks_Down_the_Psychology_of_lsquoHiddenHorrorrsquo_in_New_Video_for_gtobserver.php |title=Bloober Team Breaks Down the Psychology of \u2018Hidden Horror\u2019 in New Video for >observer_ |date=23 June 2017 |website=[[Gamasutra]] |archivedate=23 March 2018 |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20180323152118/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/pressreleases/300512/Bloober_Team_Breaks_Down_the_Psychology_of_lsquoHiddenHorrorrsquo_in_New_Video_for_gtobserver.php |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"313ctr0810\">{{cite web |url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2017-06-07-observer-is-a-game-about-going-through-peoples-apartments-and-ransacking-their-minds |title=Observer is a game about going through people's apartments - and ransacking their minds |first=Robert |last=Purchese |date=26 June 2017 |website=[[Eurogamer]] |archivedate=12 February 2018 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180212231647/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2017-06-07-observer-is-a-game-about-going-through-peoples-apartments-and-ransacking-their-minds |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Porreca-2017\">{{cite web |url=https://www.destructoid.com/observer-to-release-august-19-star-blade-runner-actor-449704.phtml |title=Observer to release August 15, star Blade Runner actor |first=Ray |last=Porreca |date=19 July 2017 |website=[[Destructoid]] |archivedate=23 March 2018 |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20180323152456/https://www.destructoid.com/observer-to-release-august-19-star-blade-runner-actor-449704.phtml |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"MCPC\">{{cite web |url=https://www.metacritic.com/game/pc/observer |title=Observer for PC Reviews |website=[[Metacritic]] |archivedate=23 March 2018 |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20180323152709/http://www.metacritic.com/game/pc/observer |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"GI\">{{cite web |url=http://www.gameinformer.com/games/observer/b/playstation4/archive/2017/08/14/pure-horror-from-the-far-flung-future.aspx |title=Observer |first=Javi |last=Gwaltney |date=14 August 2017 |website=[[Game Informer]] |archivedate=23 March 2018 |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20180323152852/http://www.gameinformer.com/games/observer/b/playstation4/archive/2017/08/14/pure-horror-from-the-far-flung-future.aspx |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"GameRev\">{{cite web |url=http://www.gamerevolution.com/review/344911-observer-review-a-mindbending-mixture-of-cyberpunk-and-horror |title=Observer Review \u2013 A Mindbending Mixture of Cyberpunk and Horror |first=Brittany |last=Vincent |date=14 August 2017 |website=[[Game Revolution]] |archivedate=23 March 2018 |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20180323153036/http://www.gamerevolution.com/review/344911-observer-review-a-mindbending-mixture-of-cyberpunk-and-horror |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"GSpot\">{{cite 