]]\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n| [[Kyoto Sanga FC|Kyoto Sanga]]\n| {{flagicon|NGR}} [[Peter Utaka]]\n| {{flagicon|NED}} [[Jordy Buijs]]\n| {{flagicon|BRA}} [[Renan Mota]]\n| {{Flagicon|BRA}} [[Junior Silva Ferreira|Juninho]]\n| \n|\n|\n|\n|-\n| [[Fagiano Okayama]]\n| {{flagicon|BRA}} [[Paulo Roberto Gonzaga|Paulinho]]\n| {{flagicon|BRA}} [[Leo Mineiro]]\n| {{flagicon|KOR}} [[Lee Yong-jae]]\n| {{flagicon|KOR}} [[Yu Yong-hyeon]]\n| {{flagicon|KOR}} [[Lee Kyeong-tae]]\n| {{flagicon|KOR}} [[Choi Jung-won (footballer)|Choi Jung-won]]\n| {{flagicon|MAS}} [[Hadi Fayyadh]]\n|\n|-\n| [[Renofa Yamaguchi FC|Renofa Yamaguchi]]\n| {{flagicon|BRA}} [[Renan dos Santos Paixao|Renan]]\n| {{flagicon|BRA}} [[Henik Luiz de Andrade|Henik]]\n| {{flagicon|BRA}} [[Iury L\u00edrio Freitas de Castilho|Iury]]\n| {{flagicon|BRA}} [[Sandro Silva de Souza|Sandro]]\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n| [[Tokushima Vortis]] \n| {{flagicon|SRB}} [[Dusan Cvetinovic]]\n| {{flagicon|BRA}} [[Diego Jara Rodrigues|Diego]]\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n| [[Ehime FC]]\n| {{flagicon|ESP}} [[Sisinio Gonzalez Martinez|Sisi]]\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n| {{sort|Avispa|[[Avispa Fukuoka]]}}\n| {{flagicon|ESP}} [[Jon Ander Serantes]]\n| {{flagicon|ESP}} [[Carlos Guti\u00e9rrez Gonz\u00e1lez|Carlos Guti\u00e9rrez]]\n| {{flagicon|ESP}} [[Juanma (footballer, born 1990)|Juanma]]\n| {{flagicon|SWE}} [[Emil Salomonsson]]\n| {{flagicon|BRA}} [[Douglas Grolli]]\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n| [[Giravanz Kitakyushu]] \n| \n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n| [[V-Varen Nagasaki]]\n| {{flagicon|BRA}} [[Caio C\u00e9sar (footballer)|Caio C\u00e9sar]]\n| {{flagicon|BRA}} [[Leandro Freire de Araujo|Freire]]\n| {{flagicon|BRA}} [[Luan Madson Gede\u00e3o de Paiva|Luan]]\n| {{flagicon|COL}} [[Victor Ibarbo]]\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n| [[FC Ryukyu]]\n| {{flagicon|CRC}} [[Danny Carvajal]]\n| {{flagicon|PRK}} [[Ri Yong-jik]]\n| {{Flagicon|BRA}} [[Felipe Pereira Tavares|Felipe Tavares]]\n| {{Flagicon|KOR}} [[Lee Ji-seong]]\n| {{flagicon|BRA}} [[Daniel Cunha Sanches|Daniel Sanches]]\n|\n|\n|\n|}\n\n==League table==\nOn March 19,decided to change format in the 2020 MEIJI YASUDA J.LEAGUE and apply exceptional rules for promotion/relegation in all categories. Apply exceptional rules below for promotion/relegation after resume (in all J1, J2 and J3 category).<ref>{{Cite press release|date=2020-03-19|url=https://www.jleague.jp/en/news/article/16863/|title=J.LEAGUE to Change Format in the 2020 MEIJI YASUDA J.LEAGUE|publisher=Official|accessdate=2020-03-21}}</ref>{{efn|promote from J3 to J2 is number of clubs to promote may change due to licensing regulations}} \n\n{{Columns\n| gapbetween = 20em\n| col1 = \n'''Promotion'''\n*No promotion in J1\n*2 clubs promote from J2 to J1\n*2 clubs promote from J3 to J2\n| col2 = \n'''Relegation'''\n*No relegations\n}}\n{{2020_J2_League_table}}\n{{notelist}}\n\n==Positions by round==\n{{#invoke:sports rbr table|table|sortable=y|legendpos=br\n\n<!--Update team positions here-->\n|team1=ALB\n|team2=VOR\n|team3=JUB\n|team4=ARD\n|team5=YAM\n|team6=JEF\n|team7=FAG\n|team8=REN\n|team9=AVI\n|team10=VAR\n|team11=ZEL\n|team12=VEN\n|team13=HOL\n|team14=EFC\n|team15=TSC\n|team16=ZWE\n|team17=SAN\n|team18=GIR\n|team19=RYU\n|team20=MON\n|team21=THE\n|team22=VER\n\n<!--Team definitions (wikilinks in table)-->\n|name_GIR=[[Giravanz Kitakyushu]]\n|name_MON=[[Montedio Yamagata]]\n|name_THE=[[Thespakusatsu Gunma]]\n|name_HOL=[[Mito HollyHock]]\n|name_ARD=[[Omiya Ardija]]\n|name_SAN=[[Kyoto Sanga FC|Kyoto Sanga]]\n|name_FAG=[[Fagiano Okayama]]\n|name_VEN=[[Ventforet Kofu]]\n|name_VOR=[[Tokushima Vortis]]\n|name_ZWE=[[Zweigen Kanazawa]]\n|name_VAR=[[V-Varen Nagasaki]]\n|name_VER=[[Tokyo Verdy]]\n|name_ALB=[[Albirex Niigata]]\n|name_REN=[[Renofa Yamaguchi FC|Renofa Yamaguchi]]\n|name_RYU=[[FC Ryukyu]]\n|name_EFC=[[Ehime FC]]\n|name_JEF=[[JEF United Chiba]]\n|name_AVI=[[Avispa Fukuoka]]\n|name_ZEL=[[FC Machida Zelvia|Machida Zelvia]]\n|name_JUB=[[J\u00fabilo Iwata]]\n|name_TSC=[[Tochigi SC]]\n|name_YAM=[[Matsumoto Yamaga FC|Matsumoto Yamaga]]\n\n|pos_ARD=   4/ 