en Reece|Helen \"Carmen Reece\" Culver]]|Al Sherrod Lambert|Maurice David Wade|Grande}}\n| extra15 = {{hlist|Samuels|Jo Blaq{{ref|a|[a]}}}}\n| length15 = 3:52\n| all_writing = \n| title1 = \n| length1 = \n| title2 = \n| length2 = \n| title3 = \n| length3 = \n| title4 = \n| length4 = \n| title5 = \n| length5 = \n| title6 = \n| length6 = \n| title7 = \n| length7 = \n| title8 = \n| length8 = \n| title9 = \n| length9 = \n| title10 = \n| length10 = \n| title11 = \n| length11 = \n| title12 = \n| length12 = \n| title16 = \n| length16 = \n| title17 = \n| length17 = \n| title18 = \n| length18 = \n| title19 = \n| length19 = \n| title20 = \n| length20 = \n}}\n\n{{Track listing\n| extra_column = Producer(s)\n| total_length = \n| headline = ''My Everything'' {{nobold|\u2013 Italian edition (bonus tracks)}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.universalmusic.it/pop/artista/discografia/?ccidp=31523324694|title=Ariana Grande My Everything Italian Edition \u2013 Album & cd \u2013  Universal Music Pop|work=universalmusic.it|accessdate=July 8, 2015}}</ref>\n| collapsed = yes\n\n| title16 = One Last Time\n| note16 = featuring [[Fedez]]\n| writer16 = {{hlist|Guetta|Kotecha|Tuinfort|Yacoub|Falk}}\n| extra16 = {{hlist|Falk|Yacoub|Ilya{{ref|a|[a]}}{{ref|b|[b]}}|Tuinfort{{ref|b|[b]}}|Kotecha{{ref|a|[a]}}}}\n| length16 = 3:18\n\n| title17 = Love Me Harder\n| note17 = with The Weeknd) (Alex Ghenea Remix\n| writer17 = {{hlist|Martin|Kotecha|Svensson|Payami|Tesfaye|Balshe}}\n| extra17 = {{hlist|Payami|Svensson|P. Carlsson{{ref|a|[a]}}|Alex Ghenea{{ref|c|[c]}}}}\n| length17 = 3:32\n\n| length18 = 4:05\n| title18 = One Last Time\n| note18 = PiZARRO Remix\n| writer18 = {{hlist|Guetta|Kotecha|Tuinfort|Yacoub|Falk}}\n| extra18 = {{hlist|Falk|Yacoub|Ilya{{ref|a|[a]}}{{ref|b|[b]}}|Tuinfort{{ref|b|[b]}}|Kotecha{{ref|a|[a]}}|PiZARRO{{ref|c|[c]}}}}}}\n\n{{Track listing\n| extra_column = Producer(s)\n| total_length = \n| headline = ''My Everything'' {{nobold|\u2013 French new edition (bonus tracks)}}<ref>{{cite 